data.description: Welcome home to this beautifully maintained, three-bedroom two-bath brick home in Morganton! The primary bedroom features a 23-foot master walk-in closet along with the second-story loft. This home is located minutes from the Morganton Heights Shopping Center as well as the North Carolina School of Science and Math. The enclosed porch is complete with a beverage bar, perfect for your holiday parties! Book your showing today!
